.TH "LIGHTNING-CHANNEL-HTLC-DENSITY-MAX" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-channel-htlc-density-max \- FEAT-2532 verb
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning channel-htlc-density-max
.SH DESCRIPTION
channel-htlc-density-max for lightning CLI (FEAT-2532).
.PP
Returns the channel with the highest HTLC count to capacity ratio.
Output: JSON from CLN with key htlc_density_max.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
